1
00:00:28,130 --> 00:00:28,760
Master.

2
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:30,630
I still have some worldly matters to settle.

3
00:00:30,630 --> 00:00:31,630
Before returning to the Eastern Wasteland,

4
00:00:31,630 --> 00:00:32,900
I want to visit my old hometown.

5
00:00:32,900 --> 00:00:34,760
In my past life, I devoted myself entirely to the sect.

6
00:00:34,760 --> 00:00:36,660
I even gave up my life for the Supreme Mystery Palace,

7
00:00:36,660 --> 00:00:38,530
but forgot the parents and family who raised me.

8
00:00:38,530 --> 00:00:40,630
In this life, I must repay them well.

9
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:43,400
Oh.

10
00:00:44,460 --> 00:00:45,460
If you want to go,

11
00:00:46,430 --> 00:00:48,260
I will accompany you.

12
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:50,960
Master,

13
00:00:52,330 --> 00:00:54,630
my parents are ordinary mortals.

14
00:00:54,730 --> 00:00:56,390
With your imposing presence,

15
00:00:56,530 --> 00:00:58,100
I'm afraid you might frighten them.

16
00:00:58,100 --> 00:00:58,730
It's fine.

17
00:00:59,060 --> 00:01:00,860
I will just conceal my aura then.

18
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:02,190
Master is so handsome.

19
00:01:02,330 --> 00:01:04,030
No, Master is so good to me.

20
00:01:04,129 --> 00:01:05,459
A grand Quasi-Emperor of the current age,

21
00:01:05,459 --> 00:01:07,930
going to such lengths to hide his identity just for me.

22
00:01:07,930 --> 00:01:11,100
[Ding. Disciple Ji Qingchen's affection has increased again.]

23
00:01:11,100 --> 00:01:13,200
[Gained 200 Destiny Fortune Points.]

24
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:16,260
Why does it feel like this disciple is hopelessly romantic?

25
00:01:16,260 --> 00:01:19,460
But these Fortune Points are really easy to farm.

26
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:29,260
What's going on?

27
00:01:29,930 --> 00:01:31,960
Why is the city so bustling today?

28
00:01:33,830 --> 00:01:34,660
Did you hear?

29
00:01:34,759 --> 00:01:38,530
Today is the wedding day of the Ji family's Fourth Miss, Ji Qingxue.

30
00:01:38,830 --> 00:01:39,530
Sigh.

31
00:01:39,530 --> 00:01:42,190
The Fourth Miss of the Ji family is a true beauty.

32
00:01:42,430 --> 00:01:43,160
At such a young age,

33
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:45,729
she joined the Luofu Sect, which is overseen by a Saint.

34
00:01:45,729 --> 00:01:46,900
What a pity.

35
00:01:47,229 --> 00:01:51,630
She caught the eye of Reverend Changqing from the neighboring Cangqing Mountain.

36
00:01:51,630 --> 00:01:55,500
Reverend Changqing is a retired Soul Formation realm expert!

37
00:01:55,700 --> 00:01:56,860
Although he is old,

38
00:01:56,860 --> 00:01:57,960
he is hale and hearty,

39
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,030
and full of energy.

40
00:01:59,130 --> 00:02:01,900
I heard he took over a hundred concubines in the past three years.

41
00:02:01,900 --> 00:02:03,830
That's an average of three a month!

42
00:02:04,830 --> 00:02:08,100
Hahaha.

43
00:02:08,100 --> 00:02:11,560
Exactly! Reverend Changqing offered a sky-high bride price,

44
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:18,360
even paying off the Luofu Sect.

45
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:21,500
Even though the Ji family didn't want to push their daughter into the fire pit,

46
00:02:21,500 --> 00:02:23,760
how could they dare offend a Soul Formation expert?

47
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:25,930
I heard the Ji family's Eldest Miss, Ji Qingchen,

48
00:02:25,930 --> 00:02:27,700
joined the Supreme Mystery Holy Land years ago.

49
00:02:27,700 --> 00:02:29,430
Because the journey is too far, she couldn't make it back.

50
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:31,960
Reverend Changqing even sighed repeatedly in public,

51
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:32,530
saying it was a pity

52
00:02:32,530 --> 00:02:34,000
that he couldn't take the Eldest Miss

53
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,860
as a concubine as well for a taste.

54
00:02:42,460 --> 00:02:43,900
Courting death.

55
00:02:57,460 --> 00:02:59,320
The auspicious time has arrived!

56
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,000
Hold on.

57
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:10,800
My name is Wang Er.

58
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,930
Nickname Goudan.

59
00:03:12,060 --> 00:03:14,300
I was originally a local thug in Wangjia Village,

60
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:15,700
idling away all day.

61
00:03:16,130 --> 00:03:17,160
My life's hobby

62
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:20,960
was flirting with the widows and the ladies washing vegetables in the village.

63
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:23,360
One day, I blindly flirted with a young girl

64
00:03:23,700 --> 00:03:25,660
and got a heavy blow from her blacksmith father,

65
00:03:25,660 --> 00:03:26,700
dying on the spot.

66
00:03:27,900 --> 00:03:29,329
When I opened my eyes,

67
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:33,090
I had unexpectedly possessed the body of this Reverend Changqing.

68
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,490
What's even better,

69
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:37,700
I also bound to a 'Get Stronger by Taking Wives' system.

70
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:43,160
As long as I keep taking concubines, I gain cultivation and aptitude feedback.

71
00:03:43,300 --> 00:03:44,660
Relying on the system,

72
00:03:44,660 --> 00:03:47,160
I rushed all the way to become a Soul Formation expert,

73
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:53,260
living an emperor's life I never dared dream of in my past life.

74
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:56,600
[Ding. Detected 'Get Stronger by Taking Concubines' type]

75
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:58,000
[Child of Destiny.]

76
00:03:58,200 --> 00:04:00,930
So this old geezer taking concubines like crazy at his age

77
00:04:00,930 --> 00:04:02,660
is because of this damn reason.

78
00:04:06,060 --> 00:04:07,800
Sister, why are you back?

79
00:04:07,930 --> 00:04:10,660
Hurry up and leave! He's a Soul Formation expert!

80
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:21,560
So you are Ji Qingxue's sister who joined the Holy Land.

81
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:25,600
What a flawless twin lotus.

82
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:28,490
Are you willing to marry me as a concubine,

83
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:31,160
to be my 108th concubine?

84
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:32,330
Humph.

85
00:04:33,659 --> 00:04:35,800
As for this pretty boy beside you,

86
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:37,300
he is just eye candy.

87
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:38,560
Tell him to get lost immediately.

88
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,690
As if you are worthy!

89
00:04:41,900 --> 00:04:45,130
He forced you to marry your sister to him as a concubine,

90
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,159
right?

91
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:51,900
Sister, he went to Luofu Sect to use threats and bribes,

92
00:04:51,900 --> 00:04:53,330
offered a sky-high bride price,

93
00:04:53,330 --> 00:04:54,560
and threatened our parents

94
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,700
that if they didn't agree,

95
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:58,360
he would wipe out our Ji family in Luoyun City.

96
00:04:59,330 --> 00:05:02,500
Old lecher, you are courting death!
